---
title: Policy Modes
description: Safe rollout modes for policies: ENFORCE, MONITOR, REPORT_ONLY.
---

> **Version:** v1.1.0  
> This page documents behavior guaranteed in TealTiger v1.1.0.


# Policy Modes

## Modes

- **ENFORCE**: block violations (non-ALLOW decisions may raise `PolicyViolationError`)
- **MONITOR**: allow but log violations
- **REPORT_ONLY**: log decisions without evaluating policy rules

## Recommended rollout

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  A[REPORT_ONLY] --> B[MONITOR] --> C[ENFORCE]
```

## Mode resolution order

Global → environment override → policy override (most specific wins).

## Production guidance

- Start new deployments in **MONITOR**
- Enforce only high-risk policies first
